This is the Java Project made in my Semester 3 as a part of the Programming Languages II Course. 
It was fun creating this game.

Its the Brick Breaker game that one used to find in Blackberry phones!


![brick breaker](https://github.com/Nikunj-Gupta/Brick-Breaker-Game/master/brick breaker.jpg)


Usage:
For Installation: Download the files and run the command < javac BrickBreaker.java > on terminal
For running the java application: Run the command < java BrickBreaker > on terminal
